title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: Output parameter is not displayed in the data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog.
SR:
1. Open the data set dialog.
2. Call a stored procedure from the Oracle database.
3. Note that the query result is stored in the output parameter as an object.
4. Check the edit data set dialog and observe that the output parameter is not displayed.
